{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 273706, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "懂了，资本论是讲手工业小作坊的", "timestamp": 1598011461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273710, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "两个人创造的总价值才多少", "timestamp": 1598011489, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273712, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "曲解了", "timestamp": 1598011494, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273713, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建议dz重修马原", "timestamp": 1598011500, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273716, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你小作坊能给工人发多少工资？发少了工人为什么不去大工厂干活？发多了你就倒闭了，你觉得你这种例子能自洽吗", "timestamp": 1598011564, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273717, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 小作坊不行，那你说说，多少人以上能保证赚钱", "timestamp": 1598011568, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273718, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不一定 按剩余价值的说法，有可能效率太低（远低于社会平均劳动效率），产出对应的平均社会劳动时间比他们必要劳动时间的价值还低，剩余价值是负的", "timestamp": 1598011570, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273730, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你效率达到社必时附近啊", "timestamp": 1598011672, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273746, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "按这个理论，更高的技术不也靠剥夺我们这种高学历的人的剩余价值弄出来的吗？资本家又不掌握技术\n那我按市场价雇几个清华毕业的人拼命剥削就一定能赚到钱了？", "timestamp": 1598011847, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273782, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "想知道dz马原多少分（笑", "timestamp": 1598012286, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273796, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你掌握生产资料么", "timestamp": 1598012444, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273810, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 不管是写字楼、服务器、数控机床还是别的，我都可以买或者租", "timestamp": 1598012557, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273811, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: A-", "timestamp": 1598012565, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273860, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 更高的技术的生产需要大量的资本（死劳动）和劳动的投入，而且见效可能会很慢。你的资金如果不够会破产", "timestamp": 1598013526, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273869, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 小手工作坊雇清华的不得赔死", "timestamp": 1598013645, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273875, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 你这么说是对的，但这恰恰说明问题在于垄断而不在于剥削，因为谁都可以雇佣一些人给自己干活", "timestamp": 1598013783, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273877, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 小作坊互联网搞创业也是小作坊嘛", "timestamp": 1598013889, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273886, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 小作坊搞互联网有几个成功的？绝大多数上不超过两三年就凉了，少部分被收购", "timestamp": 1598014103, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273895, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我问的就是，我剥削了员工的剩余价值，为什么我不但没发财还破产了？", "timestamp": 1598014266, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273898, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那是得有资本，被剥削的工人一辈子都攒不了可以用来剥削的钱，因为他们的剩余价值全被剥削光了", "timestamp": 1598014318, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273906, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 因为你的钱不够多，或者运气不够好", "timestamp": 1598014454, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273907, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 你能找到一个数，多少钱以上肯定能赚钱吗？\n那王思聪怎么还破产了？", "timestamp": 1598014482, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273914, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 小作坊的话还是劳动生产率不够", "timestamp": 1598014631, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273915, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 要是真这么剥削就完事了，我没钱，那我把一堆人的钱聚集起来搞一个大的股份公司，我们就躺着赚钱了？", "timestamp": 1598014654, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273916, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 要是作的话怎么作都能破产的", "timestamp": 1598014684, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273936, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 一堆人能有多少钱，一个工厂的工人的闲钱加起来都没有资本家的多", "timestamp": 1598015029, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 当然不只是攫取剩余价值那么简单，除了资本数量以外有别的因素决定你能不能成功地剥削", "timestamp": 1598015141, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 273957, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 那大城市的中产完全可以抱团嘛，目前也没看到。此外，白手起家的也有，大公司破产的也多得是\n所以说这个剥削的理论根本解释不通", "timestamp": 1598015465, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274037, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "啥玩意，f君说的洞主没考虑啊", "timestamp": 1598016811, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274040, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 庸俗化简单化，前提错了能得到个屁的结论", "timestamp": 1598016882, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274046, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 我先明确我的观点，社会不公平主要来自垄断而不来自“剥削”\n你来说个高雅的复杂的解释解释", "timestamp": 1598017012, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274060, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 我早就回答过了\n高效率怎么来的？是不是资本家雇（剥削）高学历的人弄的？\n如果是，那我也可以雇有水平的人", "timestamp": 1598017155, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274067, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 再说，马克思不是号称他的理论是通俗的，工人也可以懂吗？\n在您这怎么成了高知专享了还是怎么？", "timestamp": 1598017293, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274134, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有可能几家资本家最后达成了平衡，最后工人仍然是翻不了身。每个资本家为了维持自己不被压榨的地位，只能尽最大可能的压榨工人，而工人却因为剩余价值被压榨光了不能积累一点点剩余", "timestamp": 1598018467, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274142, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 在垄断的情况下，资本家反而可以给工人稍微高一点的工资，反正竞争对手一般都很弱小，可以直接将竞争对手扼杀在摇篮里", "timestamp": 1598018612, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274206, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 你不要和我说你那个理论想象中构建的图景\n事实上我观察到的就是，中产阶级很少联合起来一起办企业，办了也多半亏钱\n你说雇佣关系存在剥削，也就是创造的价值比拿到的工资多，那十个办企业的九个破产是怎么回事\n顺便说一句，企业利润高必定不会导致员工工资更高，工资由市场供需决定，企业办的再好最后也都是股东的利润", "timestamp": 1598020031, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274312, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 但大多数劳动者所在的企业还是盈利的", "timestamp": 1598021795, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 274336, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 破产的企业破产以后还会卷了钱跑了，工资都不给你发，实际上还是被剥削了", "timestamp": 1598022001, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275697, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 工人愿意学当然能懂，单发癔症那是不成了", "timestamp": 1598082042, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275757, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 你除了在这说比猪屁还没营养的话还会干什么？别在这丢人显眼，赶紧和你爸你妈一起给爹死", "timestamp": 1598083682, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 275764, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 53016, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 和你这种垃圾人说话纯属浪费我宝贵的时间，不管你在放什么屁我都不回了，滚吧", "timestamp": 1598083862, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 53016, "reply": 41, "tag": null, "text": "假如剩余价值学说是对的\n那我随便开个小作坊，雇两个人拼命压榨他们，就一定能赚到钱了？？\n懂哥帮我解释一下", "timestamp": 1598011402, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782609, "url": "", "vote": {}}}